You can deploy Vlocity OmniScripts within the Vlocity application, or within an iFrame on a Salesforce Community or external website. Once embedded, the script can be versioned, modified, and activated without reconfiguring the page.

When using OmniScript in the Lightning Console, create a new primary tab by CTRL-clicking the link for optimal experience. Add an Apex Class Permissions Checker to enable specific access to Remote Action APIs per user or profile. Deploy OmniScripts Off-Platform with OmniOut to run them outside of Salesforce on AEM, Heroku, and other Cloud Application Platforms.
